data.description: Beautiful 2/2 split floor plan with patio in desired Lake Catherine, located in Palm Beach Gardens.Sliding glass windows bring in the natural lighting and pair nicely with vaulted ceilings to brighten the interior. The split floor plan offers added privacy to the home while the screened patio is a spacious slate to create your own oasis. There is an outside storage room on the patio with a generous amount of space.  This home is conveniently located close to shopping, restaraunts and more.
